-- E.ON Cancels Plans for Plant to Compete in U.K. Carbon Capture Competition
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-10-20T08:11:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-20/e-on-cancels-plans-for-plant-to-compete-in-u-k-carbon-capture-competition.html
E.ON AG will not proceed to the next
stage of the British government’s carbon capture and storage
competition, the company said in a statement today, as its
Kingsnorth power plant “cannot meet competition  timescales.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Gavin at 
 mgavin2@bloomberg.net  